Get ready to drop it like it’s hot. Snoop Dogg is returning to Tampa this summer — and he’s bringing some friends. The High School Reunion Tour hits the MidFlorida Credit Union Ampitheatre at 6 p.m. on Aug. 12. Snoop is co-headlining the 33-date run with Wiz Khalifa. The tour lineup also includes Too $hort, Warren G and Berner. DJ Drama is also listed as a special guest. No word on whether or not Snoop is bringing bestie Martha Stewart. Tickets go on sale via Ticketmaster at 10 a.m. Friday. Citi Cardmember presale lasts from 10 a.m. Tuesday through 10 p.m. Thursday.